nodes.text: Stew was a type of food. Types of stew included eopie stew, rootleaf stew, nerf stew tikktikk stew, grassroot stew, gungan stew, root stew, orxtle stew, scavstew, topato stew, noodle stew, and chuba stew. The children at the orphan farm on Durkteel sometimes had stew for breakfast, while the Scyre warriors of Parnassos often had stew for supper.
